message.body: Hey if yall are still in the city and free tomorrow id love to see you guys. You're all invited to chill with me at maxs free because I miss you all.
I think you left already and if that's the case I better see you come winter break!!
I leave tomorrow morning and I just finished packing everything up. I'll miss you but have fun tomorrow and have a great first term and I'll see you back in Brooklyn in the winter!
